                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable.</hi>) At eight o'clock in the morning of the 8th of Sept., I saw the prisoner running with these shoes under his jacket—I caught him—one of them dropped—there was another boy with him, who got off—the prisoner said he saw a boy steal them, and he was running after him; but he was before the other boy when I stopped him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">JURY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Which dropped the shoes? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I do not know—they fell from one of them; but previous to that, I saw the prisoner give something about the size of these shoes to the other boy.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184309180101"></xptr>
